    <section id="faq">
        <div class="max-w">
            <div class="section-label">08 — FAQ</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Quick answers.</h2>

            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q">Do I need to bring my own project?</div>
                    <div class="faq-a">
                        No — we'll provide a selection of projects to choose
                        from. You just need your laptop and your development
                        environment set up. Setup instructions will arrive by
                        email before the event.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q">What if I'm new to Claude Code?</div>
                    <div class="faq-a">
                        Comfort reading and writing code is the baseline. The
                        workshop assumes you've used AI coding tools, but
                        we'll cover the fundamentals in the intro. You don't
                        need to be an expert.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q">Is there a refund policy?</div>
                    <div class="faq-a">
                        Full refund up to 7 days before the event. After that,
                        your spot can be transferred to someone else.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-q">
                        Can I expense this through my company?
                    </div>
